summary: REQUIRES DAWNGUARD. A bunch of vanilla meshes retextured with the Snow Elf texture set I've made for a mod. Most of them are dwemer pieces, with some imperial ones.
descriptionHtml:
A bunch of vanilla meshes retextured with the Snow Elf texture set I've made for a mod. Most of them are dwemer pieces, with some imperial ones. The "Off" versions of the candle and chandelier models mean they're unlit.

If you want to use them, go ahead, as long as your mod is completely free. If you charge or will be charging for it, you can't use these models. And put my name in your readme to satisfy my ego.


Credits
-------
Original models and textures: Bethesda
Modifications: Mr. C. Racer


Thanks to
